General.Name: RightCrowd Ltd
General.Description: RightCrowd Limited develops and sells physical security, safety, and compliance software solutions in North America, Europe, the Middle East, Africa, Oceania, Asia, Australia, and Latin America. It offers RightCrowd Workforce Access, a solution that automates the access control processes for employees and contractors across their lifecycle; RightCrowd Access Analytics, a software solution that maps, measures, and monitors inappropriate access permissions, and shows where access is out of compliance; RightCrowd Visitor Management, a solution that ensures safety, security, and compliance of visitors through buildings and facilities; and RightCrowd Presence Control, a solution that enables human and automated validation of security permissions and safety requirements. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Robina, Australia.
